Aku memohon...

00:06:23.829 --> 00:06:25.843
...pada Tuhan semesta alam.

00:06:35.375 --> 00:06:36.450
Berhenti.

00:06:39.455 --> 00:06:41.258
Ganti dengan ayam lain.

00:06:41.611 --> 00:06:43.017
Baik, Nyonya.

